"Record the output provided by `ethtool`, particularly noting the **master-"
"slave status**, **speed**, **duplex**, and other relevant fields. This "
"information will be useful for further analysis or troubleshooting. Once the "
"**ethtool** output has been collected and stored, move on to the next "
"diagnostic step."
